column16: Eric Hosmer grounds into a double play, second baseman Robinson Cano to shortstop Jean Segura to first baseman Danny Espinosa.   Lorenzo Cain out at 2nd.
Lorenzo Cain singles on a line drive to center fielder Jarrod Dyson.   Whit Merrifield to 2nd.
Whit Merrifield grounds into a force out, catcher Carlos Ruiz to second baseman Robinson Cano.   Cam Gallagher out at 2nd.    Whit Merrifield to 1st.
Cam Gallagher singles on a fly ball to center fielder Jarrod Dyson.
Alex Gordon flies out to center fielder Jarrod Dyson.
Alcides Escobar pops out to first baseman Danny Espinosa in foul territory.
Mike Moustakas flies out to left fielder Guillermo Heredia.
Melky Cabrera doubles (19) on a fly ball to center fielder Jarrod Dyson.   Eric Hosmer scores.
Eric Hosmer singles on a ground ball to center fielder Jarrod Dyson.   Whit Merrifield scores.    Lorenzo Cain scores.
Lorenzo Cain reaches on a force attempt, throwing error by first baseman Danny Espinosa.   Cam Gallagher scores.    Whit Merrifield to 2nd.
Whit Merrifield singles on a line drive to left fielder Guillermo Heredia.   Cam Gallagher to 2nd.
